Drbaph .matrix  
Copyright 2025 Drbaph, UK  
All Rights Reserved  

This project, **Drbaph .matrix**, is an interactive media transformation tool built using **vanilla JavaScript, HTML, CSS, and the Canvas API**. It enables users to convert images and videos into stunning dot-matrix visual effects with customizable settings, live previews, and export capabilities.

